{"tid":210858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉公廁遊蕩令壯男受驚　理大男博士生禁離港","createTime":"2017-04-21T08:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T11:43:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e624b3c2b30b18f2d2b8514a7dc2111807bc19","tid":210858,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP8rRK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP8rRK8.jpg&h=d60c9fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在香港理工大學修讀博士課程的男學生，涉嫌在公廁男廁遊蕩，令到一名壯年男子受驚，男事主與他爭執後，走出公廁找警員求助。涉案男學生事後被控一項遊蕩罪，案件今在九龍城法院提堂，法庭按辯方申請，准他暫毋須答辯，以待索取法律文件及其醫學報告後再訊，案件押後至6月2日再訊。 <br />\n<br />\n操普通話的被告劉淑利(28歲)，報稱理大學生，他被控於去年10月27日，在紅磡鶴園街公廁4樓男廁的公眾地方遊蕩，導致男子黃健鵬合理地擔心自身安全或利益。 <br />\n<br />\n控方指被告是內地居民，要求除原有500港元現金保釋，額外限制被告保釋期間不得離境，獲法庭批准。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/mobile/bkn-20170421135431144-0421_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170421%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170421135431144-0421_00822_001.html&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=3f604be6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/mobile/bkn-20170421135431144-0421_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5a75771e80a320a783a2e15cc990686a90bef495","tid":210858,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"支那仔仲要係gay佬"},{"pid":"12de0d426f6a7a12a9f0879c0b0a6475472ee0e6","tid":210858,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"28歲死大陸閪"},{"pid":"c4ff6fa0e94bf3a1804fe6e69e4b1ffee5eddc69","tid":210858,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}